&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll be joining our&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Shared Services&lt;/strong&gt; team, supporting smaller short-term rental operators with outstanding guest communication and property management services. Shared Services combine smart technology with real people to deliver 24/7 support — helping our partners provide an exceptional guest experience while growing their businesses. This role blends technology, customer service, and problem-solving in a fast-paced, remote environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;
